# get cursos
GET {{apiurl}}/cursos HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

## get curso
GET {{apiurl}}/cursos/1 HTTP/1.1

### inserir curso
POST {{apiurl}}/cursos HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Bacharelado em Agronomia",
  "sigla": "Agro",
  "descricao": "Curso de Agronomia",
  "id_coordenador":18
}

### alterar professor
PUT {{apiurl}}/cursos/8 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Bacharelado em Agronomia",
  "sigla": "Agro",
  "descricao": "Curso de Agronomia e blablabla",
  "id_coordenador":18
}

### excluir professor
DELETE {{apiurl}}/cursos/7 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json